title: Newsmaker: On song again, the redoubtable Mrs Fadnavis - The Indian Express
content: Newsmaker: On song again, the redoubtable Mrs Fadnavis  The Indian Express
description: Maharashtra Chief Minister Uddhav Thackeray's swipe and Devendra Fadnavis' own admission shows that in or out of power, 43-year-old Amruta Fadnavis can't be ignored
